'''山姆·肯德里克斯'''（{{lang-en|Sam Kendricks}}，{{bd|1992年|9月7日||}}）是一名美国男子[[撑杆跳高|撑杆跳高]]运动员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flashresults.com/2015_Meets/Outdoor/06-25_USATF/026-1_compiled.htm|title=Men Pole Vault SR|work=flashresults.com|accessdate=June 27, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924034223/http://www.flashresults.com/2015_Meets/Outdoor/06-25_USATF/026-1_compiled.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以5.85米的成绩赢得2016年[[里约奥运会|里约奥运会]]男子撑杆跳高[[铜牌|铜牌]]。2019年7月27日，肯德里克斯以6.06米的成绩打破了美国撑杆跳高歷史纪录<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.teamusa.org/News/2019/July/27/Sam-Kendricks-Sets-American-Record-And-Wins-Record-Sixth-Consecutive-Pole-Vault-National-Title|title=Sam Kendricks Sets American Record And Wins Record Sixth Consecutive Pole Vault National Title|last=Shinn|first=Peggy|date=July 27, 2019|website=Team USA|access-date=July 30, 2019|archive-date=2021-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210730113512/https://www.teamusa.org/News/2019/July/27/Sam-Kendricks-Sets-American-Record-And-Wins-Record-Sixth-Consecutive-Pole-Vault-National-Title|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.iaaf.org/news/report/sam-kendricks-pole-vault-606m|title=Kendricks tops 6.06m in Des Moines{{!}} News {{!}} iaaf.org|website=www.iaaf.org|language=en|access-date=July 30, 2019|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024063429/https://www.iaaf.org/news/report/sam-kendricks-pole-vault-606m|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

